title: Guernsey to feature in prime time national television (States of Guernsey)
text: ( Source : States of Guernsey ) Thursday 08 October 2015 Guernsey will feature on primetime national television on next week ( 13th October and 18th October ) in the Channel 4 series 'Homes by the Sea'. The island is the focus of the episode
